02:36:19,430 --> 02:36:22,780
He twisted her wrist again, and she fell.

2014
02:36:22,780 --> 02:36:25,190
'You're nothing but a common...'

2015
02:36:25,190 --> 02:36:27,910
'Leave me alone!'

2016
02:36:27,910 --> 02:36:28,910
she cried.

2017
02:36:28,910 --> 02:36:32,771
'You have no right to touch me or speak to
