2019
02:36:36,552 --> 02:36:40,150
The whole of Cornwall knows it.

2020
02:36:40,150 --> 02:36:42,870
Your game is over, Uncle Joss.

2021
02:36:42,870 --> 02:36:47,211
I've been to Launceston today to inform against
you.'

2022
02:36:47,211 --> 02:36:54,080
A loud cry came from the group of men; they
pressed forward, shouting at her and questioning,

2023
02:36:54,080 --> 02:36:59,420
but the landlord swore at them, waving them
