2042
02:38:15,900 --> 02:38:19,641
The pedlar pulled at the horse.

2043
02:38:19,641 --> 02:38:26,710
Joss Merlyn stood for a moment, looking at
Mary with a foolish smile, then he pulled

2044
02:38:26,710 --> 02:38:31,960
her towards the carriage, threw her on the
seat in the corner, and then, leaning out

2045
02:38:31,960 --> 02:38:37,510
of the window, he shouted to the pedlar to
whip the horse up the hill.

2046
02:38:37,510 --> 02:38:43,311
His cry was repeated by the men who ran beside
him, and some of them jumped onto the step

2047
02:38:43,311 --> 02:38:47,780
and held onto the empty driver's seat and
hit the horse with sticks.

2048
02:38:47,780 --> 02:38:54,900
The animal sped up the hill in its fear, dragging
