2049
02:38:54,900 --> 02:38:56,090
Jamaica Inn was all lit up.

2050
02:38:56,090 --> 02:39:01,550
The doors and the windows were wide open.

2051
02:39:01,550 --> 02:39:06,750
The landlord placed his hand over Mary's mouth
and forced her back against the side of the

2052
02:39:06,750 --> 02:39:07,750
carriage.

2053
02:39:07,750 --> 02:39:10,811
'You'd inform against me, would you?

2054
02:39:10,811 --> 02:39:15,710
You'd run to the law, and have me swinging
