2055
02:39:15,710 --> 02:39:18,521
All right then!

2056
02:39:18,521 --> 02:39:25,360
You shall stand on the shore, Mary, and you
shall watch for the daylight and the coming

2057
02:39:25,360 --> 02:39:26,711
in of the tide.

2058
02:39:26,711 --> 02:39:31,211
You know what that means, don't you?

2059
02:39:31,211 --> 02:39:34,271
You know where I'm going to take you?

2060
02:39:34,271 --> 02:39:38,300
You think you're not afraid of me, don't you?

2061
02:39:38,300 --> 02:39:44,870
