2076
02:40:48,551 --> 02:40:54,130
The carriage had been stopped in a narrow
valley with high banks on either side, and

2077
02:40:54,130 --> 02:40:57,300
the horse had been taken away.

2078
02:40:57,300 --> 02:41:03,311
The valley appeared to slope down sharply,
