02:44:43,050 --> 02:44:49,300
She had no idea of the time; it was three,
perhaps four, in the morning, and the darkness

2128
02:44:49,300 --> 02:44:53,490
would give no sign of breaking for many hours.

2129
02:44:53,490 --> 02:44:58,141
Once more, the rain came down through the
curtain of mist, and it seemed as if she could

2130
02:44:58,141 --> 02:45:03,510
hear the sea on every side of her and there
