Mary could bear no more.

2156
02:46:56,380 --> 02:47:02,860
She got to her feet and ran out across the
beach, shouting and crying, waving her hands

2157
02:47:02,860 --> 02:47:08,280
above her head, lifting her voice in her battle
against the sea and the wind, which threw

2158
02:47:08,280 --> 02:47:10,710
it back to her.

2159
02:47:10,710 --> 02:47:15,090
Someone caught hold of her and forced her
down on to the beach.

2160
02:47:15,090 --> 02:47:17,540
She was stepped on and kicked.

2161
02:47:17,540 --> 02:47:24,490
Her cries died away as a rough cloth covered
