2162
02:47:24,490 --> 02:47:28,150
and tied together, the rope cutting into her
flesh.

2163
02:47:28,150 --> 02:47:35,630
They left her then, with the waves sweeping
towards her not 20 yards away, and as she

2164
02:47:35,630 --> 02:47:41,450
lay there helpless, she heard the cry that
had been hers become the cry of others, and

2165
02:47:41,450 --> 02:47:43,540
fill the air with sound.

2166
02:47:43,540 --> 02:47:50,550
This cry rose above the noise of the sea,
and was seized and carried by the wind; and

2167
02:47:50,550 --> 02:47:57,000
with the cry came the terrible sound of splitting
and breaking wood.

2168
02:47:57,000 --> 02:48:03,870
Mary saw the great black shape that had been
the ship roll slowly on its side in two parts.

2169
02:48:03,870 --> 02:48:09,890
From it, little black dots fell one by one
