2177
02:48:40,870 --> 02:48:46,010
One of them lit a fire in the corner by the
rocks, the flames burning strongly in spite

2178
02:48:46,010 --> 02:48:47,880
of the rain.

2179
02:48:47,880 --> 02:48:53,600
The goods from the sea were dragged across
the beach and piled beside it.

2180
02:48:53,600 --> 02:48:58,990
The fire spread a yellow light over the scene
