2191
02:49:48,100 --> 02:49:50,930
The sky and the sea turned grey.

2192
02:49:50,930 --> 02:49:55,460
At first, the men did not notice the change.

2193
02:49:55,460 --> 02:50:02,660
And then Joss Merlyn himself lifted his great
